audit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:13:| Course Leader | `Dashboard`, `Queue History`, `Calendar / Timetable`, `Data Entry Hub`, course pages, student pages, faculty profile button | Session login and `POST /api/session/role-context`; `GET /api/academic/bootstrap`; course-leader-owned offering reads/writes; `tasks`, `task-placements`, `calendar-audit`, `meetings`, and offering config routes are scope-gated; `student-shell` and `risk-explorer` require active-run + student scope | `scheme-setup` and `entry-workspace` are launched from course/upload actions; `student-history`, `student-shell`, and `risk-explorer` are launched from student cards and proof controls | Visible UI is broader than backend write scope. The page helper can show a route, but the server still checks offering ownership and student enrollment. |
